{
  "3277350": {
    "name": "光域",
    "steam_appid": 3277350,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >上古时期，祖龙元凤相争，两败俱伤，其身体元神化作世间八域，而人类便生于八域之中，祖龙元凤虽身死，但其元神经久不消，由此于八域之中孕育出不少能人异士。而仙族不在八域之中，独处仙界，与人类互不干涉。直至一日，一位身份不明的少年打通了八域同仙界之间的通道，致使无数贪图利益之人意图涌入仙界，仙界大能因此降下谪仙以下仙罚，而谪仙以身化像于光域之中布下心魔幻境，以此遏制光域中各路高手的成长脚步，而主角身为光域中的一员，突破层层幻境</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/ac832424c874fa4e2a84e84c6df4c720.avif?t=1758553816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras_big/ac832424c874fa4e2a84e84c6df4c720.avif?t=1758553816 width=800 height=217 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/d251b131d244aeb103d21a0475a791e1.poster.avif?t=1758553816\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/d251b131d244aeb103d21a0475a791e1.webm?t=1758553816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/d251b131d244aeb103d21a0475a791e1.mp4?t=1758553816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏里有6种丹药6种特质不同的选择会带来不一样的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丹药：击败小怪有20%的概率掉落丹药，可以交互捡起或者替换丹药栏的丹药，只能携带1个。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >特质:特质是在地牢探索玩法中的强力道具，可以通过房间奖励、商店购买、击杀怪物等方式获得特质，特质的效果仅在地牢探索玩法中生效，且在完成探索或探索失败后不会保留。当每个房间探索完毕之后都会随机刷新2个特质，可以任选一个放入特质栏或替换一个饰品。<br>玩家在地牢探索玩法中至多可以装备五件特质，每一件特质会有一项属性提升和两项祝福；每件特质有稀有度之分，分别为普通（蓝）、稀有（红）、史诗（紫）、传奇（金）；稀有度越高的特质，提供的属性加成越高，特质的稀有度不会影响祝福的效果，特质的稀有度可以在锻炉中进行升级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/974ca00f4bcb3cc2e4f3b76e340b003e.avif?t=1758553816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras_big/974ca00f4bcb3cc2e4f3b76e340b003e.avif?t=1758553816 width=800 height=217 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/291debd6e6b88dbf4d19fd772d0d3f6d.poster.avif?t=1758553816\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/291debd6e6b88dbf4d19fd772d0d3f6d.webm?t=1758553816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/291debd6e6b88dbf4d19fd772d0d3f6d.mp4?t=1758553816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >天赋系统可以强化角色的弱点或者你有更好的想法强化角色本来就突出的特色。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/690f8fc1cecbfee3b39b97d9491f8eeb.avif?t=1758553816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras_big/690f8fc1cecbfee3b39b97d9491f8eeb.avif?t=1758553816 width=800 height=217 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/ae4d9b6834e15cc78e1b4b1812c90b27.avif?t=1758553816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras_big/ae4d9b6834e15cc78e1b4b1812c90b27.avif?t=1758553816 width=800 height=462 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同的地图不同的怪物和boss。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/51f2c7d10a8d53ef4cd7c853aa91d8bc.poster.avif?t=1758553816\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/51f2c7d10a8d53ef4cd7c853aa91d8bc.webm?t=1758553816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/51f2c7d10a8d53ef4cd7c853aa91d8bc.mp4?t=1758553816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >墨家机关道部分展示。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/f40142e6bbcf35e98974ff95f4dc29f0.poster.avif?t=1758553816\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/f40142e6bbcf35e98974ff95f4dc29f0.webm?t=1758553816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/f40142e6bbcf35e98974ff95f4dc29f0.mp4?t=1758553816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/77c6e6b3efbb65335b3c81e314d78d94.poster.avif?t=1758553816\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/77c6e6b3efbb65335b3c81e314d78d94.webm?t=1758553816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/77c6e6b3efbb65335b3c81e314d78d94.mp4?t=1758553816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无尽模式以及关卡强化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/7f48de4d3f387050d91ab75351de62c7.avif?t=1758553816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras_big/7f48de4d3f387050d91ab75351de62c7.avif?t=1758553816 width=800 height=217 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/c64e0dbac0c84e3a3708497a8e6b4255.poster.avif?t=1758553816\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/c64e0dbac0c84e3a3708497a8e6b4255.webm?t=1758553816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/c64e0dbac0c84e3a3708497a8e6b4255.mp4?t=1758553816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >按键操作自定义根据你自己的习惯来吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/65e5b21cf9e313e33358997345172eaa.avif?t=1758553816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras_big/65e5b21cf9e313e33358997345172eaa.avif?t=1758553816 width=800 height=217 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/9da9afdaa488064dbc58eba08fb7aee9.poster.avif?t=1758553816\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/9da9afdaa488064dbc58eba08fb7aee9.webm?t=1758553816\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/9da9afdaa488064dbc58eba08fb7aee9.mp4?t=1758553816\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升等级解锁不同的技能搭配让挑战更有趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/c9abe580204965272d98a47740216863.avif?t=1758553816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras_big/c9abe580204965272d98a47740216863.avif?t=1758553816 width=800 height=282 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/ef5484bc34575bc79afa807548d96faf.avif?t=1758553816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras_big/ef5484bc34575bc79afa807548d96faf.avif?t=1758553816 width=800 height=585 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/0106ab391b5fbf2bbd9223e48bd51fb9.avif?t=1758553816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras_big/0106ab391b5fbf2bbd9223e48bd51fb9.avif?t=1758553816 width=800 height=585 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/bc772f3a9cc20617e3f79526d103b297.avif?t=1758553816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras_big/bc772f3a9cc20617e3f79526d103b297.avif?t=1758553816 width=800 height=585 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/c35b3ee26df6c56f17465b8a66aa16d6.avif?t=1758553816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras_big/c35b3ee26df6c56f17465b8a66aa16d6.avif?t=1758553816 width=800 height=585 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras/5053ed6e4ede463050e28d2b41bbf148.avif?t=1758553816\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3277350/extras_big/5053ed6e4ede463050e28d2b41bbf148.avif?t=1758553816 width=800 height=585 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
